description._content: Original Caption: Pregame Discussion by the Coach for Cathedral Senior High School Football Players Prior to a Game at Johnson Park in New Ulm Minnesota. Physical Fitness Is Stressed in This Community of German Descendants. The Town Has a Turner Club for Youth Interested in Gymnastics. Turnvereins Or Turner Clubs, Began in Germany in the 1800's and Stress Health through Exercise, Particularly Gymnastics the Club Claims to Be One of the Co-Founders of New Ulm.
